                    "comments": [
                        {
                            "type": {
                                "id": 202,
                                "en": "Substance criteria comment",
                                "fr": "Commentaire sur le statut de déclaration de la substance"
                            },
                            "comment": "Technical Contact, Company Coordinator: Fraser Forsythe SE Manager\nPlease be advised that the Emission Factor used to calculate the PM10 and PM 2.5 emissions are predicated on EPA document: “AP 42, Fifth Edition, Compilation of Air Pollutant Emission Factors, Volume 1: Stationary Point and Area Sources”; which is not based on the type of combustion process employed by the cryogenic heaters used by our process to re-gasify LNG. We wish therefore to reserve the right to revise the emission values reported based on further review of emissions from the submerged combustion methodology of water heating for vaporization of LNG.\n\nRegards,\n\nFraser\n"
                        }
                    ],
